      "created": "2020-12-15T16:42:25.926+0000",
      "description": "The goal of this Jira is to provide an optional plugin to apply runC container transformations. Enabling runC container transformations will provide an easy way to apply site specific customizations to all containers.\r\n\r\nAn example of one transformation that many clusters may need could be a Kerberos transformation. This would apply cluster Kerberos configurations and mount them to all runC containers that are submitted, without requiring users to manage them within their own images.",
